{"tid":2034201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[突破盲腸]陳曼琪話自己喺人大入紙建議,韓正又話上年十月中央已經拍板,邊個講大話？","createTime":"2020-05-25T05:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T09:38:12.000Z","uid":134683,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cc67696f9c646e345e8ea8f1051db9377f4908d0","tid":2034201,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"陳曼琪亦在日前稱會書面建議北京訂立《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》，指應直接依《基本法》第18條，將國家安全法納入《基本法》附件三，不需要經立法會審議，直接在香港實施。<br />\n［蘋果日報］2020年5月20日<br />\n<br />\n港區人大代表、<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯葉國謙今天引述韓正指，中央審視反修例風波後，考慮到港府難以透過本地立法推動23條，因此早在去年四中全會已經決定引入「港版國安法」</span>，重申不應低估中共的決心，北京已預料反對派或激進示威者會繼續發起「暴亂」。<br />\n［蘋果日報］2020年5月24日"},{"pid":"7483f01f427f166e6c543d27c9a0c53428985367","tid":2034201,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08c6edcf2c57b877563d999e8e2a1a693a5af81","tid":2034201,"uid":288979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"個邊講啲野洗咩咁上心"},{"pid":"9fe86cd2ef2f9a903b041135390ca51e47e0e36d","tid":2034201,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c6100ffa3f34824ae2e0262c8b3c7cff2c57cb","tid":2034201,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1b89af73557ae460e3feb13d7abad198bb4c79","tid":2034201,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"cbf56787dccc559be181629949821b6f98816c59","tid":2034201,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc78b1bf6c760fb1be0c